aught by Adobe Certified Instructor Daniel Scott will walk you through the very basics, up to the shortcuts and techniques the pros use. You'll even work on mini projects and assignments you can add to your portfolio. Another crash course, led by life coach and best-selling instructor Joe Parys, explores speed manipulation and transitioning, while Invert Media Founder Bryan Guerra's course shows you how to add special effects, graphics, text, and more to your videos.\nBeyond editing video footage, you'll also take a deep dive into audio mixing and voice processing. In a course led by Tomas George, a music producer and audio engineer, you'll learn professional audio processing tools and techniques, like EQ essentials, DeNoise, DeReverb, compression, and more. By the end of all six courses, the complicated interface of Premiere Pro won't look so intimidating. Heck, you may even be able to launch that YouTube channel you've been dreaming up.Â \nEach course in this bundle is valued at $199 a pop. But for a limited time, you can snag the whole collection for just $29.99 (97% off).\n\n            \n              \n                \n              \n            \n            \n              The Adobe Premiere Pro CC Video and Audio Production Course Bundle â€” $29.99\n              See Details"},"image":"https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fstory%252Fthumbnail%252F118738%252F923ea3c8-076d-4825-90c9-cc7611de4ef7.jpeg%252F950x534__filters%253Aquality%252880%2529.jpeg?signature=LFgUN9GbcdSbTNX5uHE1kTdkhoc=&source=https%3A%2F%2Fblueprint-api-production.s3.amazonaws.com","feature_image":"https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fstory%252Fthumbnail%252F118738%252F923ea3c8-076d-4825-90c9-cc7611de4ef7.jpeg%252F1438x0.jpeg?signature=bPFxyXnsm4bis5hp6u6RjdDzbZc=&source=https%3A%2F%2Fblueprint-api-production.s3.amazonaws.com","responsive_images":[{"image":"https://mondrian.mashable.com/uploads%252Fstory%252Fthumbnail%252F118738%252F923ea3c8-076d-4825-90c9-cc7611de4ef7.jpeg%252F3